            "es": "4.5 Pólizas especializadas — Joint vs Survivorship, Indexed UL, Modified/Graded, Family, Juvenile",
            "en": "4.5 Specialized Policies — Joint vs Survivorship, Indexed UL, Modified/Graded, Family, Juvenile"
